  <brief_title>Influence of the Sleep Pattern in Patients Submitted to Bariatric Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Influence of the Sleep and Chronotype Pattern in Metabolic, Anthropometric and Biochemical Responses in Patients Submitted to Bariatric Surgery</official_title>
